posting_body: ['The Cielo Apartments', 'Visit Our Community Today!', '5951 University Ave NE', 'Fridley, MN 55432', 'show contact info', 'The Cielo is proudly managed by Peak Living.', 'At Peak Living, our mission is to provide the highest quality property management services in the industry.', 'We achieve this through our greatest asset;
